{"format": "tiptap/v1", "updatedAt": "2026-06-22T04:37:39.915Z", "doc": {"type": "doc", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Versioning experiments"}, {"type": "text", "text": " is the practice of treating ML experiments as immutable, versioned artifacts—by snapshotting the "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "codebase state, data version, hyperparameters, pipeline configuration, and resulting metrics"}, {"type": "text", "text": " for each experiment run—so you can reproduce, compare, and restore any past experiment at any time, rather than just logging metrics in a dashboard."}]}, {"type": "blockquote", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Key difference:"}, {"type": "text", "text": " Tracking experiments = logging metrics, parameters, and artifacts in a dashboard. Versioning experiments = codifying experiments as code so logs are "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "always connected to the exact data, code, and pipeline that produced them"}, {"type": "text", "text": "."}]}]}, {"type": "horizontalRule"}, {"type": "image", "attrs": {"src": "data:image/svg+xml;base64,", "alt": "Versioning Experiments — concept overview"}}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 2}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "What experiment versioning is (conceptually)"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Experiment versioning brings together:"}]}, {"type": "bulletList", "content": [{"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Code versioning"}, {"type": "text", "text": " (Git commits)"}]}]}, {"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Data versioning"}, {"type": "text", "text": " (DVC or similar)"}]}]}, {"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Pipeline versioning"}, {"type": "text", "text": " (DVC pipeline config)"}]}]}, {"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Parameter and metrics versioning"}, {"type": "text", "text": " (text files like "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "code"}], "text": "params.yaml"}, {"type": "text", "text": ", "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "code"}], "text": "metrics.json"}, {"type": "text", "text": ")"}]}]}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "This creates a "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "single atomic record"}, {"type": "text", "text": " for each experiment that captures everything needed to reproduce it."}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Core idea:"}, {"type": "text", "text": " “Experiment versioning treats experiments as code. It saves all metrics, hyperparameters, and artifact information in text files that can be versioned.” "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "link", "attrs": {"href": "https://dvc.org/blog/ml-experiment-versioning/", "target": "_blank", "rel": "noopener noreferrer nofollow", "class": "text-brand-600 underline dark:text-brand-400", "title": null}}], "text": "dvc"}]}, {"type": "horizontalRule"}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 2}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Why versioning matters (vs. just tracking)"}]}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 3}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Problem with tracking-only approaches"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "When you only "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "track experiments"}, {"type": "text", "text": " (e.g., with a dashboard):"}]}, {"type": "bulletList", "content": [{"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "You log metrics, parameters, Git commit, etc."}]}]}, {"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "But to "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "reproduce"}, {"type": "text", "text": " a result later, you must:"}]}]}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "- Manually trace back to the exact code commit - Manually restore the exact data version - Manually reconstruct the pipeline"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Tracking alone doesn’t guarantee you can "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "restore"}, {"type": "text", "text": " the experiment easily."}]}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 3}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "How versioning solves this"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Experiment versioning:"}]}, {"type": "bulletList", "content": [{"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Connects experiment logs to exact data, code, and pipeline"}, {"type": "text", "text": " automatically"}]}]}, {"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Let you "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "reproduce or restore"}, {"type": "text", "text": " an experiment with a "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "single command"}]}]}, {"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Enables:"}]}]}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "- "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Reproducibility"}, {"type": "text", "text": ": Run the same experiment again with the same setup - "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Comparison"}, {"type": "text", "text": ": See how metrics changed across iterations - "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Iteration"}, {"type": "text", "text": ": Start from a previous experiment and make "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "only the necessary changes"}]}, {"type": "blockquote", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "“Versioned reproducibility means tracking changes to the experiment state. DVC can determine what changes were introduced by the experiment and only run what’s necessary.”"}]}]}, {"type": "horizontalRule"}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 2}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "What gets versioned for each experiment"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "A complete experiment version includes:"}]}, {"type": "table", "content": [{"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableHeader", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Element"}]}]}, {"type": "tableHeader", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "What’s captured"}]}]}, {"type": "tableHeader", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Example"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Code"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Git commit hash of the training/evaluation code"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "code"}], "text": "abc123def"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Data"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Data version (hash, DVC version, dataset ID)"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "code"}], "text": "data-v2.3"}, {"type": "text", "text": ", "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "code"}], "text": "dvc-ref-xyz"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Pipeline"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Pipeline configuration (DVC pipeline steps)"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "code"}], "text": "dvc.yaml"}, {"type": "text", "text": " pipeline definition"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Parameters"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Hyperparameters in text files"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "code"}], "text": "params.yaml"}, {"type": "text", "text": " with "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "code"}], "text": "lr: 0.001"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Metrics"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Resulting metrics in text files"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "code"}], "text": "metrics.json"}, {"type": "text", "text": " with "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "code"}], "text": "accuracy: 0.92"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Artifacts"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Model files, logs, visualizations"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "code"}], "text": "model.pkl"}, {"type": "text", "text": ", "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "code"}], "text": "confusion_matrix.png"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Environment"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Library versions, OS, GPU type"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "code"}], "text": "torch 2.1"}, {"type": "text", "text": ", "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "code"}], "text": "python 3.10"}]}]}]}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "This creates a "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "reproducibility chain"}, {"type": "text", "text": " linking results to the exact code and data."}]}, {"type": "horizontalRule"}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 2}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Experiment versioning with DVC (Data Version Control)"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "DVC is the most popular tool for "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "experiment versioning"}, {"type": "text", "text": " (as opposed to just tracking)."}]}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 3}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "How DVC experiment versioning works"}]}, {"type": "orderedList", "attrs": {"start": 1, "type": null}, "content": [{"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Initialize DVC in a Git repo"}, {"type": "text", "text": ":"}]}]}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "``"}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "code"}], "text": "bash dvc exp init -i "}, {"type": "text", "text": "`"}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "code"}], "text": " This creates a structured project with: - "}, {"type": "text", "text": "params.yaml"}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "code"}], "text": " (parameters) - "}, {"type": "text", "text": "metrics.json"}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "code"}], "text": " (metrics) - "}, {"type": "text", "text": "dvc.yaml` (pipeline config)"}]}, {"type": "orderedList", "attrs": {"start": 1, "type": null}, "content": [{"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Structure your code"}, {"type": "text", "text": ":"}]}]}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "- Training script reads parameters from "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "code"}], "text": "params.yaml"}, {"type": "text", "text": " - Training script writes metrics to "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "code"}], "text": "metrics.json"}]}, {"type": "orderedList", "attrs": {"start": 1, "type": null}, "content": [{"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Run experiments"}, {"type": "text", "text": ":"}]}]}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "``"}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "code"}], "text": "bash dvc exp run "}, {"type": "text", "text": "`` DVC: - Caches pipeline outputs - Versioned metrics, parameters, and artifacts - Links them to the Git commit"}]}, {"type": "orderedList", "attrs": {"start": 1, "type": null}, "content": [{"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Reproduce an experiment"}, {"type": "text", "text": ":"}]}]}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "``"}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "code"}], "text": "bash dvc exp restore <experiment-ref> "}, {"type": "text", "text": "`` This restores: - Exact code version - Exact data version - Exact parameters and metrics Without needing to manually reconstruct anything."}]}, {"type": "orderedList", "attrs": {"start": 1, "type": null}, "content": [{"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Compare experiments"}, {"type": "text", "text": ":"}]}]}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "- DVC can show which experiments changed, what changed, and only re-run what’s necessary"}]}, {"type": "horizontalRule"}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 2}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Experiment versioning in LLM/Evaluation workflows"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "For LLM applications, experiment versioning is critical because evaluation is "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "highly sensitive to code changes"}, {"type": "text", "text": ":"}]}, {"type": "bulletList", "content": [{"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Modified prompt template"}]}]}, {"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Updated metric threshold"}]}]}, {"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Changed data preprocessing step"}]}]}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Ragas Experiment Versioning Principle"}, {"type": "text", "text": " addresses this by:"}]}, {"type": "bulletList", "content": [{"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Creating "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Git snapshots"}, {"type": "text", "text": " for each evaluation experiment"}]}]}, {"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Associating each experiment run with the "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "exact codebase state"}, {"type": "text", "text": " that produced it"}]}]}]}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 3}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Procedure: version an experiment"}]}, {"type": "codeBlock", "attrs": {"language": "text"}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "procedure version_experiment(experiment_name, commit_message, repo_path, create_branch, stage_all):\n  1. Locate Git repo\n  2. Stage changes (if any)\n  3. Create commit with experiment name\n  4. Create branch: ragas/{experiment_name}\n  5. Return commit hash as version identifier"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "This creates a "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "reproducibility key"}, {"type": "text", "text": " (commit hash) linked to the experiment name."}]}, {"type": "horizontalRule"}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 2}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Model versioning vs. experiment versioning"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "These are related but distinct:"}]}, {"type": "table", "content": [{"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableHeader", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Aspect"}]}]}, {"type": "tableHeader", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Model Versioning"}]}]}, {"type": "tableHeader", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Experiment Versioning"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "What it versions"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Iterations of trained ML models"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Iterations of experiments (training runs)"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Focus"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Systematic management of model iterations"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Codifying experiments as reproducible units"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Includes"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Model artifacts, metadata, deployment state"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Code, data, pipeline, parameters, metrics, artifacts"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Purpose"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Traceability of model evolution, backtracking changes"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Reproducing and comparing experiments over time"}]}]}]}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Model versioning is a "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "subset"}, {"type": "text", "text": " of experiment versioning: each model version typically comes from one (or more) experiment versions."}]}, {"type": "horizontalRule"}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 2}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Best practices for experiment versioning"}]}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 3}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "1. Use a meaningful version naming system"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Example 4-number system:"}]}, {"type": "bulletList", "content": [{"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Project version"}, {"type": "text", "text": ": "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "code"}], "text": "x"}, {"type": "text", "text": " (e.g., "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "code"}], "text": "1"}, {"type": "text", "text": " for first time)"}]}]}, {"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Data version"}, {"type": "text", "text": ": "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "code"}], "text": "y"}, {"type": "text", "text": " (increment when data changes)"}]}]}, {"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Algorithm version"}, {"type": "text", "text": ": "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "code"}], "text": "z"}, {"type": "text", "text": " (increment per algorithm change)"}]}]}, {"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Minor changes"}, {"type": "text", "text": ": "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "code"}], "text": "w"}, {"type": "text", "text": " (hyperparameters, tweaks)"}]}]}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Version: "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "code"}], "text": "x.y.z.w"}, {"type": "text", "text": " (e.g., "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "code"}], "text": "1.2.3.1"}, {"type": "text", "text": ")"}]}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 3}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "2. Treat experiments as code"}]}, {"type": "bulletList", "content": [{"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Store metrics, parameters, and artifacts in "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "text files"}, {"type": "text", "text": " that can be versioned"}]}]}, {"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Use Git for code, DVC for data and pipeline "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "link", "attrs": {"href": "https://dvc.org/blog/ml-experiment-versioning/", "target": "_blank", "rel": "noopener noreferrer nofollow", "class": "text-brand-600 underline dark:text-brand-400", "title": null}}], "text": "dvc"}]}]}]}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 3}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "3. Automate logging"}]}, {"type": "bulletList", "content": [{"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Use automated logging to capture metadata in real time"}]}]}, {"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Reduce manual effort and risk of oversight"}]}]}]}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 3}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "4. Use atomic runs"}]}, {"type": "bulletList", "content": [{"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Each experiment run should capture:"}]}]}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "- Source code - Configuration - Upstream requirements (datasets) - Generated output\n- All in a "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "single place"}, {"type": "text", "text": ", not scattered across systems"}]}, {"type": "horizontalRule"}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 2}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Key takeaways"}]}, {"type": "bulletList", "content": [{"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Experiment versioning"}, {"type": "text", "text": " treats experiments as code by snapshotting code, data, pipeline, parameters, and metrics so you can reproduce and restore any experiment with a single command."}]}]}, {"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Unlike "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "tracking-only"}, {"type": "text", "text": " (dashboards), versioning ensures experiment logs are "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "always connected"}, {"type": "text", "text": " to the exact data, code, and pipeline that produced them."}]}]}, {"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "DVC"}, {"type": "text", "text": " is the main tool for experiment versioning, enabling:"}]}]}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "- "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "code"}], "text": "dvc exp init"}, {"type": "text", "text": " to structure projects - "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "code"}], "text": "dvc exp run"}, {"type": "text", "text": " to run experiments - "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "code"}], "text": "dvc exp restore"}, {"type": "text", "text": " to reproduce past experiments\n- For LLM evaluation, experiment versioning creates "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Git snapshots"}, {"type": "text", "text": " linked to commit hashes as reproducibility keys.\n- Best practices: use meaningful version naming, automate logging, and treat each experiment as an atomic unit capturing code, data, config, and output."}]}]}}